data.description: The seller is offering a generous 4,000.00 for rate buydown, closing costs or improvements. This Spacious home is a must see and is a well sought after Savannah Floor plan. Excellent  location wihin a gated community with a tree lined view from the upstairs balcony, view of trees and a cozy eating area just off the dining room. The kitchen has a upgraded backsplash , under the counter lighting, wood stairway steps and upstairs hallway. Built in ceramic bench in the master  shower . Heated and cooled outside storage closet. The front porch carries dusk to dawn lights and matching modern remote LED ceiling fans in the living room and all bedrooms, The dining room has a beautiful Chandelier. The seller has added wood decking to the attic space for additonal storage, Rain Tree shower head in the master bath. The upstairs has a new wi-fi thermostat and all new metal gear dampner controls. In wall wire management for all tv locations to hide wires and led lighting inside and out  This home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Beautiful hard wood floors and granite kitchen counters. This home is beautifly landscaped and is in a quiet gated communitly with community pool, , dock access to St Andrews bay. Watch the sunset over the bay from your kayack or from your upstairs Balcony.
